390
00:21:18,190 --> 00:21:19,760
Jingzhao gave the dragon core.

391
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:21,150
I will return her one.

392
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:22,520
Houchi.

393
00:21:23,150 --> 00:21:23,960
Are you crazy?

394
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,880
