brings disaster to the Heavenly Palace.

428
00:22:40,430 --> 00:22:41,000
Mother,

429
00:22:41,190 --> 00:22:41,910
in this case,

430
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,550
we may wait for God Gu Jun

431
00:22:43,910 --> 00:22:46,070
