484
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:31,240
Don’t worry.

485
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:32,430
Trust me.

486
00:25:05,190 --> 00:25:05,760
Master.

487
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:06,720
