510
00:25:53,430 --> 00:25:54,120
It doesn’t matter.

511
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:14,550
Houchi!

512
00:26:16,270 --> 00:26:16,910
Houchi.

513
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,190
Houchi,

514
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,520
what are you doing?

515
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:03,240
That’s...

516
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,720
