562
00:31:51,910 --> 00:31:53,000
not a toy for you.

563
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:56,150
He has the right to make his own choice.

564
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:57,190
And

565
00:31:58,030 --> 00:32:01,030
